data.description: Comfortable 4 bedroom brick home in Kings Crossing. Southside find with an open floor plan, spacious kitchen, 3 car garage and backyard ready to entertain guests on game nights. Tall ceilings and split, large bedrooms. Jack-n-Jill bath. New HVAC Nov 2023. One year warranty included.
